{"tid":1991582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東怡旅遊、實惠旅遊被撤銷會籍及牌照","createTime":"2020-04-27T13:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T14:43:37.000Z","uid":50386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7e45b37827e8960b32d01ecae469e717f926e39","tid":1991582,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:44:21.000Z","msg":"#旅遊消息 <br />\n香港旅遊業議會(議會)獲悉旅行代理商註冊處今天(4月27日)撤銷以下兩家旅行社的牌照後，隨即終止其會籍：<br />\n<br />\n東怡旅遊有限公司 / Eastrip Travel Company Limited (營業名稱：東怡機票 / Eastrip Travel；牌照號碼：351601)；以及<br />\n 環球酒店網絡有限公司 / Hotel Everywhere Company Limited (營業名稱：實惠旅遊 / Net Travel；牌照號碼：352543)。<br />\n<br />\n受影響旅客請向相關機構辦理賠償及退款手續。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"http://www.tichk.org/public/website/b5/news/2020_04_27z/html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tichk.org%2Fpublic%2Fwebsite%2Fb5%2Fnews%2F2020_04_27z%2Fhtml&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4W58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=9d8d695c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tichk.org/public/website/b5/news/2020_04_27z/html</a>"},{"pid":"dcc8520473f4b6b2efdf647e40fc56b9af8d5bd3","tid":1991582,"uid":215766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T14:26:16.000Z","msg":"同gogo travel &amp;wefly 同一個腦細 吳x廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd703e5016ab3d8652fe3be62acba25a257714f7","tid":1991582,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T14:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kJ7Ufw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1kJ7Ufw.gif&h=ee5bd90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新登記選民截止日期：2020年5月2日<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4W58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=82bf3c9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jL0uupX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjL0uu